lead_paragraph: A'ja Wilson scored a career-best 31 points and had 12 rebounds to help No. 3 South Carolina beat No. 14 Texas 76-67 on Thursday night in the SEC/Big 12 Challenge.

headline.print_headline: Wilson Has 31 Points, No. 3 South Carolina Tops No. 14 Texas
